# Public Google Calendar API key for the homepage custom calendar.
# - Read-only; only reads PUBLIC calendars.
# - Exposed in client JS (it's a "PUBLIC_" var) — this is expected for a
#   browser-side key. Restrict it in Google Cloud Console:
#     * Application restriction: HTTP referrers → https://wcsmn.com/* (and your
#       preview/localhost origins).
#     * API restriction: Google Calendar API only.
# Without this key the homepage calendar shows a graceful notice and falls back
# to the Google embed for no-JS users.
PUBLIC_GOOGLE_CALENDAR_API_KEY=
